summary: kinda sucks how the phandom could live off their slow burn smut fanfiction and phan speculation for years to come and be...
body: kinda sucks how the phandom could live off their slow burn smut fanfiction and phan speculation for years to come and be satisfied, because ultimately dan and phil’s presumed relationship status is what makes many people stick around, but the general dan and phil youtube audience gets absence, inactivity and the type of content that you feel like dan and phil don’t really enjoy putting out most of the time. whether it’s intentional or not, dan and phil’s actions weed out those who don’t read phanfic after phanfic after phanfic, don’t repost 2009 tweets and don’t participate in the ‘dan and phil are totally fucking’ discourse.
